  "prompt": "How did the Green Arrow get his powers?",
  "response": "The Green Arrow, also known as Oliver Queen, is a popular superhero in the DC Comics universe. Unlike many other superheroes, Green Arrow does not have superpowers. Instead, he relies on his exceptional skills in archery, martial arts, and his keen intellect. His abilities come from intense training and experience rather than any supernatural or superhuman origin.\n\nIn the origin story, Oliver Queen is a wealthy playboy and entrepreneur who is stranded on a deserted island after a shipwreck. During his time on the island, he hones his skills in archery and survival. When he eventually returns to civilization, he adopts the persona of the Green Arrow to fight crime and injustice, using a variety of trick arrows and gadgets to aid him in his endeavors.",
